OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782082982
OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FUS Vice President JD Vance landed in
OL,8,FSwitzerland on Sunday to help formally
OL,9,Flaunch negotiations with Iranian
OL,10,Fleaders over curbing Tehran's nuclear
OL,11,Fprogram and building out the fragile
OL,12,Finterim deal to end the war in Iran.
OL,14,FVance and his wife, second lady Usha
OL,15,FVance, arrived in the country just
OL,16,Fbefore 6 am local time, according to
OL,17,Fhis office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782082982
OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe framework was signed last week,
OL,8,Fand now top US and Iran negotiators
OL,9,Fare in a 60-day sprint to reach an
OL,10,Fagreement on the technical details
OL,11,Fthat hold massive implications for the
OL,12,Fworld economy and global security.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782082982
OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FYet the first days of that two-month
OL,8,Fperiod were complicated by the heavy
OL,9,Fexchange of fire in Lebanon between
OL,10,FIsrael and the Iranian-backed militant
OL,11,Fgroup Hezbollah ` and by the
OL,12,Fsubsequent announcement by Iran's
OL,13,Fmilitary that it had closed the Strait
OL,14,Fof Hormuz, the vital waterway that
OL,15,Ftransits a fifth of the world's traded
OL,16,Foil and natural gas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782082982
OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FVance had originally been slated to
OL,8,Farrive in Switzerland on Friday, but
OL,9,Fhis departure from the United States
OL,10,Fwas delayed after fighting escalated
OL,11,Fin Lebanon, and Iranian officials
OL,12,Fcancelled plans to attend the talks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
