PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782082982
OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FUS Central Command disputed Iran's
OL,8,Fclaim that it had once again shuttered
OL,9,Fthe strait and said US forces
OL,10,Fcontinued to monitor the situation to
OL,11,Fensure traffic continues to flow
OL,12,Fthrough the waterway. Vance has said
OL,13,Fthat millions of barrels of oil have
OL,14,Fmoved through the strait in recent
OL,15,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782082982
OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FVance departed the US just after
OL,8,FIranian state TV said Iran's
OL,9,Fnegotiators had arrived in
OL,10,FSwitzerland. Tehran's negotiators
OL,11,Finclude parliamentary speaker Mohammad
OL,12,FBagher Qalibaf and Foreign Minister
OL,13,FAbbas Araghchi, along with central
OL,14,Fbank and oil officials.
OL,16,FThe US vice president joins special
OL,17,Fenvoy Steve Witkoff and Jared Kushner,
OL,18,FPresident Donald Trump's son-in-law,
OL,19,Fwho have already been on the ground to
OL,20,Fbegin sifting through the technical
OL,21,Fdetails of the nuclear talks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782082982
OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe talks between the US and Iran will
OL,8,Falso include Pakistani Prime Minister
OL,9,FShehbaz Sharif and army chief Field
OL,10,FMarshal Asim Munir, as well as Qatari
OL,11,Fmediators.
OL,13,FWhile Vance said he planned to be in
OL,14,FSwitzerland for just "a day or two,"
OL,15,Fleaving much of the detailed
OL,16,Fnegotiations to be spearheaded by
OL,17,FWitkoff and Kushner, his role in the
OL,18,Ftalks has heightened the scrutiny of
OL,19,Fthe vice president at a time when he's
OL,20,Factively considering a 2028
OL,21,Fpresidential campaign.
OL,26,@vD@VOUvD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
