OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FTrump and Vance have come under
OL,13,Fsearing criticism from parts of their
OL,14,Fown party for the deal, with
OL,15,FRepublican hard-liners unfavourably
OL,16,Flikening it to a nuclear agreement
OL,17,Fsigned by the Obama administration
OL,18,Fthat Trump and the GOP have insisted
OL,19,Fdid nothing to actually terminate
OL,20,FIran's nuclear program.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
