PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782082982
OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe agreement signed by Trump and
OL,8,FIranian President Masoud Pezeshkian
OL,9,Fimmediately allows Tehran to sell its
OL,10,Foil freely and paves the way for Iran
OL,11,Fto tap into billions of dollars in
OL,12,Fassets that are currently frozen.
OL,14,FIt also calls for Iran to dilute its
OL,15,Fstockpile of highly enriched uranium,
OL,16,Fbelieved to be buried under nuclear
OL,17,Fsites that were targeted in US strikes
OL,18,Flast summer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782082982
OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe agreement says commercial vessels
OL,8,Fcan pass through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,9,Ffor 60 days without a charge, but does
OL,10,Fnot preclude future fees imposed by
OL,11,FIran.
OL,13,FTrump made his own threat on Saturday
OL,14,Fto levy US tolls on the strait if
OL,15,Fthere is no deal with Iran in 60 days,
OL,16,Finsisting in a social media post that
OL,17,Fthe money would be for "services
OL,18,Frendered as the Guardian Angel to the
OL,19,Fcountries of the Middle East."
OL,26,@yD@XOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
