OL,3,CUS-Iran negotiations to begin in
OL,4,CSwitzerland as Iran closes Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FFurther complicating matters, neither
OL,8,FIsrael nor Hezbollah are signatories
OL,9,Fto the deal between the US and Iran,
OL,10,Fand Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,11,FNetanyahu has vowed to keep his forces
OL,12,Fin southern Lebanon until any threat
OL,13,Fto Israel is eliminated. Hezbollah has
OL,14,Frefused to halt its attacks unless
OL,15,FIsrael commits to withdrawing from
OL,16,FLebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
